At the turn of the century, the atmosphere is enlivened by the presence of photos, the exhibition's mobile application reveals the convocations of individual works of art with photographs taken by the painter with his own camera for creative purposes.
Meanwhile, the Finnish-Latvian friendship society "Rozentāls-seura", named after the Latvian classic, at the Latvian National Museum of Art simultaneously offers the first stop of a small informative traveling exhibition "With a Gaze in Finland, with a Heart in Latvia".
