The transformation of the former Kemeri sanatorium into a five-star hotel will cost 22 million euros.
The transformation of the former Kemeri sanatorium into a five-star hotel "Park Hotel Ķemeri" will cost 22 million euros, Gita Želve, a representative of the future hotel manager SIA "Park Hotel Ķemeri", tells LETA agency.
The creation of the hotel is the first stage of the renovation of the former Kemeri sanatorium.
