However, the reconstruction took a long time.
In turn, in the annual report for 2010, it was also stated that "Ominasis" regularly communicates with the hotel operator "Kempinski", which continues to provide daily technical control in the sanatorium "Ķemeri", and already in 2011 the reconstruction of the future hotel "Ķemeri" will definitely be "completed" and preparations for the opening of the hotel of the "Kempinski" chain will immediately begin.
